videos.description: Maurice Calloo grabs his teammate's missed dunk to throw it down himself, putting Oklahoma State ahead of Oklahoma 15-14.
videos.headline: Calloo bails out teammate with a slam

videos.description: Oklahoma's Kristian Doolittle leaps and rejects a shot underneath the rim.
videos.headline: Doolittle gets big block under rim

videos.description: Oklahoma's Jamal Bieniemy tosses it to Brady Manek inside the post for the flush.
videos.headline: Manek gets fed for the jam
